    <h5 class="panel-title g-font-size-30--xs g-font-size-32--md g-font-weight--700 {% if autoheight == 'false' %} g-ver-center--lg {% endif %} g-padding-r-100--xs g-padding-r-150--md">
        Southeast Sections<br >
        <p>General sections shortcode to be used on any pages.</p>
    </h5>
</div>
<div id="collapse-sections-lava-shortcodes" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel"
aria-labelledby="sections-lava-shortcodes" aria-expanded="false" style="height: 0px;">
    <div class="panel-body"> <!-- START: panel-body -->
        <p>
        Three different layouts available. Check out this link for examples: <a href="https://rock.secc.org/page/2616" target="_blank">https://rock.secc.org/page/2616</a>
        </p>
        <br />
        <div>
        <p>
            The "{%- raw -%}{[ seccsection ]}{%- endraw -%}" block configuration has the following options:
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li><p><strong>layout</strong> - Set the layout of your choosing. The options available are: 'left', 'right', or 'center'. <i>Default is <b>'right'</b>.</i><br></p></li>
            <li><p><strong>image</strong> - Set the image URL here. It can be absolute or relative.</p></li>
            <li><p><strong>imagewidth</strong> - Set the image max width. <i>The default is <b>500px</b>.</p></li>
        </ul>
        </div>
        <br />
{%- raw -%}
<b>Right layout example: </b>
<pre>
<code class="language-markup">
{[ seccsection layout:'right' image:'this/is/an/image/url.jpg' ]}
    Content/copy goes here
{[ endseccsection ]}
</code>
</pre>
{%- endraw -%}
        <br />
    </div>
</div> 
</div> 
